840
00:49:25,279 --> 00:49:26,413
Sampai jumpa.

841
00:49:29,149 --> 00:49:32,252
Dulu dia sangat kerena. Kenapa
dia membagi-bagikan selebaran?

842
00:49:35,489 --> 00:49:37,358
"Cabang Kota Baru
SC Food and Beverage"

